<p>This subpage of the <a href="Wikipedia_Manual_of_Style" title="Wikipedia:Manual of Style">Manual of Style</a> contains guidelines for writing and editing clear, encyclopedic, attractive, and interesting articles on <a href="Mathematics" title="Mathematics">mathematics</a>. For matters of style not treated on this subpage, follow the main Manual of Style and its other subpages to achieve consistency of style throughout Wikipedia.</p>
