</ul>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Wikipedia_Manual_of_Style_Mathematics&action=edit&section=39.php.html" title="Edit section: General information">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="General_information">General information</span></h3>
<ul>
